(17,1,E'place',E'Batumi',E'Black sea resort Batumi first day',NULL,E'2019-08-25 09:00:00+00',E'2019-08-25 20:00:00+00',E'Batumi is the go-to holiday destination for Both Georgians (only the richer ones) and lots of foreigners. This place is especially populair among Turkish people fond of throwing money at gambling machines.',5,E'2019-11-17 11:27:30.299498+00'),
