(24,1,E'day trip',E'Just outside Tblisi',E'Mtskehta Monestary and Jvari Church',NULL,E'2019-08-29 09:00:00+00',E'2019-08-29 20:00:00+00',E'Mt skehta is the holy church of Georgia. The country  has a strong catholic following, and this place is a must visit for them. ',6,E'2019-11-17 11:27:30.299498+00'),
(25,1,E'day trip',E'2 hours from Tblisi',E'David Garaja Monestary',NULL,E'2019-08-30 07:00:00+00',E'2019-08-30 20:00:00+00',E'Although people told me before hand the most of it is closed due to "tensions with our friends to the east". I deemed it still worth visiting. In the end im not sure i would\'ve done it again, but I am happy I did go.',6,E'2019-11-17 11:27:30.299498+00'),
(26,1,E'place',E'Tblisi',E'Last day: Old Town?!',E'Some find it weird that i leave the historic and arguable the best place to visit for last. I guess i agree. But generally I prefer to work from the outside in. First the outskirts, the surrounding places, and things to do. And then at end go inside the city, explore more there.',E'2019-08-31 07:00:00+00',E'2019-08-31 20:00:00+00',NULL,6,E'2019-11-17 11:27:30.299498+00'),
